Yes, you can track your order through the IKEA website. On the 'Track and manage your order' page (https://www.ikea.com/us/en/customer-service/track-manage-order/) there is a tracking form that requires:
1. **Order number** – the number you received when you placed the order.
2. **Email address or phone number** – the contact information used for the purchase.
After entering these details, click the **"Track order"** button to view the status of your order.
No additional login is required unless you want to view all your past orders.


